This is the implementation of a forward chaining inference engine in PHP language which can be used to build expert systems.

To test,

1. Copy all these files to a web accessible directory of a web server that has PHP support.
2. Create a MySQL database. Load the two sql files in the 'sql' directory to the database.
3. Edit config.php file and specify database access details.
4. Access the index.php from a web browser. Specify the URL based on your web server and installed directory.
5. Test the samples.

Visit this URL for details: http://www.deadschool.com/phpexpertsystem

This software is unlicensed. Details are in the UNLICENSE file.


